---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Heating & Furnace Repair | String Prairie Heating & Air"
	description="Professional heating and furnace repair in Bastrop County. Fast, reliable heater repair from String Prairie Heating & Air. Call (512) 924-9744."
>
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Heating & Furnace Repair</h1>
			<p>Keep your home warm with reliable heating repair services</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="service-content">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="service-intro">
				<h2>Expert Heating System Repair</h2>
				<p class="lead">
					When temperatures drop in Central Texas, a working heater is essential. String Prairie Heating & Air provides professional heating and furnace repair services throughout Bastrop County. Our technicians are experienced with all types of heating systems and can quickly diagnose and repair problems.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="service-grid">
				<div class="service-main">
					<h3>Heating Systems We Service</h3>
					<div class="systems-grid">
						<div class="system">
							<h4>Gas Furnaces</h4>
							<p>The most common heating system in Texas homes. We repair all major brands.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="system">
							<h4>Heat Pumps</h4>
							<p>Efficient systems that provide both heating and cooling from one unit.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="system">
							<h4>Electric Furnaces</h4>
							<p>Safe and reliable heating for homes without gas service.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="system">
							<h4>Dual Fuel Systems</h4>
							<p>Hybrid systems combining a heat pump with a gas furnace backup.</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h3>Common Heating Problems We Fix</h3>
					<ul class="service-list">
						<li>
							<strong>No Heat</strong>
							<p>Pilot light issues, ignition problems, or thermostat malfunctions can prevent your system from producing heat.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Insufficient Heat</strong>
							<p>Dirty filters, ductwork issues, or failing components can reduce heating output.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Short Cycling</strong>
							<p>When your furnace turns on and off frequently, it indicates a problem that needs attention.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Strange Noises</strong>
							<p>Banging, squealing, or rumbling sounds often indicate worn parts or airflow issues.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>Yellow Pilot Light</strong>
							<p>A yellow flame instead of blue may indicate a carbon monoxide risk requiring immediate attention.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>High Energy Bills</strong>
							<p>A heating system working harder than necessary will increase your utility costs.</p>
						</li>
					</ul>

					<h3>Our Repair Process</h3>
					<div class="process-steps">
						<div class="step">
							<span class="step-number">1</span>
							<h4>Safety Check</h4>
							<p>We inspect for gas leaks and carbon monoxide issues first.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<span class="step-number">2</span>
							<h4>Diagnosis</h4>
							<p>We thoroughly test your system to identify the exact problem.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<span class="step-number">3</span>
							<h4>Repair</h4>
							<p>We fix the issue using quality parts and proven techniques.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="step">
							<span class="step-number">4</span>
							<h4>Testing</h4>
							<p>We verify safe, proper operation before leaving.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="service-sidebar">
					<div class="cta-box">
						<h3>Need Heating Repair?</h3>
						<p>Don't let a broken heater leave you in the cold. Contact us today for fast, professional service.</p>
						<a href="https://book.housecallpro.com/book/String-Prairie-Heating--Air/df82ded280ce43f4a9ee6ee6d36aef76?v2=true" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">ðŸ”– Book Online</a>
						<a href="tel:5129249744" class="btn btn-secondary">Call (512) 924-9744</a>
					</div>

					<div class="info-box warning">
						<h4>Safety First</h4>
						<p>If you smell gas or suspect a carbon monoxide leak, leave your home immediately and call your gas company or 911.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="info-box">
						<h4>Why Choose Us?</h4>
						<ul>
							<li>Family-owned and operated</li>
							<li>Experienced technicians</li>
							<li>Safety-focused service</li>
							<li>Upfront, honest pricing</li>
							<li>Quality parts and workmanship</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="info-box">
						<h4>Service Areas</h4>
						<p>We provide heating repair in:</p>
						<ul>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/bastrop">Bastrop</a></li>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/rosanky">Rosanky</a></li>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/smithville">Smithville</a></li>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/elgin">Elgin</a></li>
							<li><a href="/service-areas/paige">Paige</a></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="emergency-banner">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>Heating Emergency?</h2>
			<p>A broken heater during cold weather is more than uncomfortableâ€”it can be dangerous. Call us for fast response.</p>
			<a href="tel:5129249744" class="emergency-btn">Call (512) 924-9744</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-blue) 0%, var(--primary-blue) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 5rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.page-header p {
		font-size: 1.35rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.service-content {
		padding: 5rem 0;
		background: white;
	}

	.service-intro {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.service-intro h2 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		line-height: 1.8;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.service-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 350px;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.service-main h3 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		font-size: 1.75rem;
		margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.systems-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.system {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 1.25rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-red);
	}

	.system h4 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.system p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.service-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.service-list li {
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background: var(--bg-light);
		border-radius: 8px;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.service-list li strong {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.service-list li p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 300;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.process-steps {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.step {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.step-number {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		width: 40px;
		height: 40px;
		background: var(--primary-blue);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.step h4 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.step p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin: 0;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.service-sidebar {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.cta-box {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
		border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-red);
	}

	.cta-box h3 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.cta-box p {
		color: var(--text-dark);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.btn {
		display: block;
		padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-red) 0%, var(--dark-red) 100%);
		color: white;
	}

	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: white;
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		border: 2px solid var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.btn-secondary:hover {
		background: var(--primary-blue);
		color: white;
	}

	.info-box {
		background: var(--bg-light);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);
	}

	.info-box.warning {
		border-left-color: #f59e0b;
		background: #fef3c7;
	}

	.info-box.warning h4 {
		color: #b45309;
	}

	.info-box.warning p {
		color: #92400e;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.info-box h4 {
		color: var(--dark-blue);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.info-box ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.info-box li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		color: var(--text-dark);
		font-weight: 300;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
	}

	.info-box li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}

	.info-box a {
		color: var(--primary-blue);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.info-box a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.emergency-banner {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-red) 0%, var(--dark-red) 100%);
		color: white;
		padding: 4rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.emergency-banner h2 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.emergency-banner p {
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		opacity: 0.95;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.emergency-btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
		background: white;
		color: var(--accent-red);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 700;
		border-radius: 50px;
		transition: all 0.3s;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.emergency-btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-3px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
	}

	@media (max-width: 968px) {
		.service-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.systems-grid,
		.process-steps {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.page-header h1 {
			font-size: 2.25rem;
		}
	}
</style>
